snippet.title: Amber Heard Admits To Hitting Johnny Depp in Audio Recording (Transcribed).
snippet.description:
We've decided to transcribe the audio of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard that was leaked this weekend (Jan 31st) to the best of our ability.  

We think this needs to get out there in as many ways possible.

Please share far and wide as the audio and transcription speak volumes.

We will be discussing our thoughts on this on a separate video.

#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard

If you like what you see, please like, subscribe and share!
